I know quite a few people that are Bipolar I and also OCD. Maybe you
should talk to your doc. I am diagnosed with Bipolar II but I have had
a couple of hypermanic episodes in the distant past. I used to fixate
on certain things and it was explained to me that, because I show
certain symptoms of OCD (there is also a big family of history of
OCD), even though it is not sufficient to warrant a diagnosis and
meds, the hypermania will tend to aggravate it. That's just what my
doc told me... shrug. Take it for what it's worth I guess.
</POST>
