YES!! Absolutely.  I have seen this dramatically in my life.  And once
you get a little help from the meds, you can start working on it in a
behavioral therapy type of way too.  But I couldn't even begin to do
that without the meds. Tell your doctor about it.  An SSRI might help,
a mood stabilizer might help, a benzo might help...something out there
should be able to at least help take some of the edge off of it.
